swaplogger (0.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * The iterative average FPS counter now ignores the first zero-length frame
    after a reset
  * The windowed average (afps_N) counter now includes all samples within the
    window
  * Made iterative average FPS (afps) counter more accurate
  * Added option to display non-rounded results (-w)
  * The min/max FPS counters are now also valid before the first manual reset
  * Fixed the help switch (-h) in the launcher script

 -- Sami Kyöstilä <sami.kyostila@nokia.com>  Tue, 11 May 2010 16:30:02 +0300

